description: Try our easy to follow Triple Chocolate & Caramel Brownies recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Triple Chocolate & Caramel Brownies Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Whisk caramel in a small bowl with milk to loosen. Add dollops randomly over brownie then use a skewer to swirl through chocolate mixture. Bake for 1820 minutes then cool in tray for 1 hour. Refrigerate or cut and serve.
